Disarm - offensive trick
------------------------------------------------------------
A swashbuckler soon becomes adept at relieving enemies of
their weapons. A failed attempt will cause the target to
become enraged and attack, but a successful attempt will
cause it to drop its weapon. There is no effect on targets
using natural weaponry--claws, fists, fangs, etc.

GL:  6
SP: 40
command:  sdisarm <target> (defaults to opponent if in combat)
duration: instant
